Post.title: Cch s dng Git
Post._content:
## 1. Add

### 1.1 Add tt c thay i

```bash
git add .
```

### 1.2 Add mt file no 

```bash
git add /projects/file1.txt
```

### 1.3 Add mt folder no 

```bash
git add /projects
```

## 2. Commit

```bash
git commit -m "Tm tt ni dung thay i"
```

## 3. Push

```bash
git push origin master
```
